  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "1500DS Spirits: Mahjong V (widely used English translation. Original name is \"1500 DS spirits: 麻雀V\") is a Japan exclusive mahjong game. It is part of a large series of Nintendo DS titles which focus on table games all labeled 1500DS Spirits and created and published by Tasuke Co. Ltd.. This game is a special addition version of 1500DS Spirits: Vol 1 Mahjong and has extra added features compared to that game. This game used 1500DS Spirits: Vol 1 Mahjong as a base for this game so it has some similarities to this game including borrowed modes and assets.",
